<title>byn ydyk rạḥty</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - byn ydyk rạḥty byn ydyk ạ̉ḥtmy

[V2]
 ạ̉nt mlyky sydy rạʿy ḥyạty wmrsẖdy
 1- byn ydyk kyf ạ̉kẖạf wạ̉nt rby wmnqdẖy
 tʿyn ḍʿfy tḥnw ʿlyã tḥyṭ byã tqwdny
 2- byn ydyk ạ̉ṭrḥ nfsy fạ̉nt sẖmsy mstqbly
 wạtẖq fy sẖkẖṣk fy ʿmq ḥbk tfyḍ bkẖyrk tgẖmrny
 3- hạ ạ̉nạ rby sẖhwẗ qlby ạ̉n ạ̉ḥyạ ʿmry fy ṭạʿtk
 ạ̉mlk ḥyạty wạ̉smʿ ṣlạty wạ̉smw bḥby lạ̉ʿrfk</lyrics>
